THEY’RE SETTING IT OFF IN MSG!!!!

Smackdown opens with the Bloodline minus Jacob Fatu. They are going to make an entrance when they’re jumped by Orton, Cody and Kevin Owens!!!!

Theyre brawling all over the arena and at one point Kevin Owens leaps off a barricade and puts Tonga Loa through a table

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d74870f0-1b91-4def-9c9d-c76b9b3edb48/20240628_171723.jpg?format=original)

Cody, Orton and Kevin Owens refuse to leave the ring until they can end the Bloodline for good.

Nick Aldis has to bring out the NYPD to get them to cooperate

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/836e2005-e7b6-4601-9142-1ac988447c89/20240628_173048.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_TIFFANY STRATTON DEF. JADE CARGILL AND CANDICE LERAE TO EARN HER SPOT IN MITB_**
    

Jade Cargill was distracted by Nia Jax and taken out by Indi Hartwell

Nia Jax and Tiffany have really bonded into this new partnership

* * *

