*   ## **_LA KNIGHT DEF. LOGAN PAUL AND SANTOS ESCOBAR TO EARN A SPOT IN MITB_**
    

After the match, Logan Paul and Indiana Pacers’ Tyrese Haliburton try to jump LA Knight but New York Knicks’ Jalen Brunson comes in with a steel chair to even the odds

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a68409a1-c77d-4089-81dd-c8bc751f2cd8/557784598c18265742bc23094df8318d.jpeg?format=original)

*   ## **_Naomi def. Blair Davenport and Indi Hartwell._**
    

Naomi pinned Indi after Jade Cargill interfered to get revenge on Hartwell for interfering earlier in the night in the Triple Threat she took part in.

